metadata.name: Bomb Effect
metadata.description:
Axstone depicts a crowd scene brimming with technological relics, alien characters, and delightful objects, in her signature muted color palette.

Selin Çinar (aka Axstone) is a Turkish artist and illustrator. Her client list includes Apple, Mercedes Benz, and Nike, and she’s been featured in publications including Vogue, and Hifructose.
